{"tid":1516201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大辱華白人大媽不被指控 但罵她或會被控罪","createTime":"2019-08-29T13:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T13:18:52.000Z","uid":299826,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"64b35a977d6398be819501230a50a467d090e317","tid":1516201,"uid":299826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"週二(8月27日)加拿大BC省大溫哥華烈治文皇家騎警表示，數天前在當地一個停車場使用種族歧視字眼辱罵華人的白人女子，將不會被刑事指控。 據本地英文媒體CBC報導，這起案件發生於上週五(8月23日)，地點是烈治文市3號公路上的一個停車場，該白人女子由於泊車而同一個帶著孩子的華人 母親徐女士(Amy Xu)爭執，並用種族歧視字眼嘲笑對方。 徐女士拿出手機拍攝，然後向皇家騎警報了案。<br />\n<br />\n 經過了三天的調查，騎警方面最終決定，將不對該白人女子提出刑事指控。<br />\n<br />\n 騎警發言人帕瑪(Sunny Parmar)表示，雖然事件令人感到不安，但是經過仔細調查和搜證，並諮詢過BC省檢控服務處(BC Prosecution Service)的意見後，決定不予起訴。<br />\n<br />\n 該發言人還強調，在本地的社交媒體上，有很多人對此事的反應和激烈。 如果有人發表了過激言論，或進行網絡欺凌，則可能被視為刑事罪行。 警方固然理解很多列治文居民對此事非常反感，但是不希望有人過了界。<br />\n<br />\n 儘管騎警並沒有透露該白人女子的姓名，但是網民們早已將其&ldquo;人肉&rdquo;了出來。 她名叫沃爾德曼(Carla Waldman)。<br />\n<br />\n CBC早前曾就此事採訪沃爾德曼。 她承認自己泊車的時候的前保險槓接觸了對面徐女士的汽車，但表示對自己的說過的話不後悔，因為對方&ldquo;不是好人&rdquo;，而自己也不是種族主義者。<br />\n<br />\n 來源：<a href=\"http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/racist-rant-not-facing-charges-1.5261976\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Fbritish-columbia%2Fracist-rant-not-facing-charges-1.5261976&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=55ecae80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/racist-rant-not-facing-charges-1.5261976</a>"},{"pid":"09904fa238a8e8b623cbceeb9f4bb7fa7fb0a6f5","tid":1516201,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:10:51.000Z","msg":"叫China man 啦，佢地都係咁叫自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25beed74009e6a3c30f8cb164f7728cc8a7bdd1","tid":1516201,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dsM1x0y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdsM1x0y.jpg&h=f8690967&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13eda7f840901ae4d6a2dc1950ffe77b0fe59b8f","tid":1516201,"uid":53672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:13:58.000Z","msg":"真正愛國既中國人係唔會移民架!呢d移民係漢奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a723ab0e7d47db93b9ec2b7c2ea3eeee88a785d","tid":1516201,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d25beed74009e6a3c30f8cb164f7728cc8a7bdd1","tid":1516201,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dsM1x0y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdsM1x0y.jpg&h=f8690967&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe630d8d645903d3c133251275683edb25d01bcf","tid":1516201,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:18:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}